## Registrant Post-Response {#req-resp}

The *Registrant* MUST validate the signature of the OME Token returned by the OME and SHOULD validate all signatures found in the response claim.

If satisfied then the *Registrant* may proceed to provision/onboard the now registered keys and related artifacts for use.
